vd - Video Downloader

USAGE:
    vd

DESCRIPTION:
    Download videos from the queue. Processes all queued videos
    one by one, downloading them according to their metadata
    (audio extraction, profiles, etc.).

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-videos-audio-format FORMAT
        Audio format for extraction (default: aac)

    -conf-videos-youtube-download-cmd CMD
        YouTube download command (default: yt-dlp)

    -conf-videos-youtube-video-download-options OPTIONS
        Download options for video files (default: "-f bestvideo[height<=1080]+bestaudio/best[height<=1080] --recode-video mp4 --audio-format aac")

    -conf-videos-download-path PATH
        Path where videos are downloaded

    -conf-videos-video-player CMD
        Video player command for watching

EXAMPLES:
    vd
